execute in base directory (this will generate LLVM bitcode files for each Montage tool in ./bin/)
  make
  
rename each file to <filename>.bc in ./bin/ and execute on each file
  emcc -O3 -s WASM=1 bin/<file>.bc -o bin/<file>.html
  
